          <li><a href="verb-causative-form-saseru.1#ichidan-verbs" id="markdown-toc-ichidan-verbs">Ichidan Verbs</a></li>
          <li><a href="verb-causative-form-saseru.1#irregular-verbs" id="markdown-toc-irregular-verbs">Irregular Verbs</a></li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li><a href="verb-causative-form-saseru.1#the--short-form" id="markdown-toc-the--short-form">The 〜さす Short Form</a></li>
