      <li><a href="verb-causative-form-saseru.1#with-transitive-and-intransitive-verbs" id="markdown-toc-with-transitive-and-intransitive-verbs">〜させる with Transitive and Intransitive Verbs</a></li>
      <li><a href="verb-causative-form-saseru.1#the-causative-passive-" id="markdown-toc-the-causative-passive-">The Causative-Passive 〜させられる</a></li>
